test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert -25 == -5
 +  where -25 = <built-in function prod>([-5, -1, -5])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (0 == 3)
 +  where 0 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c7c5538b340>([-5])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7c7c5538b340> = [[1, -5], [1, -5, 1], [-5, 1], [-5, 1, -5], [1, -5], [1, -5, 1], ...].count
